  libgee-0.8-2,
  libjsonrpc-glib-1.0-1
Recommends: fonts-font-awesome
Description: General purpose keybinding viewer
 Remontoire reads keybinding specifications via a specific 
 string format and displays them in a one-level-deep tree
 structure suitable for tiling window managers such as i3.

